{"tid":332484,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論]其實暴雨同暴風信號應否實行分區制？","createTime":"2017-07-23T04:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T08:22:02.000Z","uid":35839,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8f4184f30c8428d0b24013c3328802255c7223","tid":332484,"uid":35839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:40:38.000Z","msg":"最近成日都見到唔少post巴絲打屌大交合&quot;水浸都係黃雨&quot;/&quot;掛八號波即刻細風左&quot;之類，而又的確好多時候大家（特別係新界人）永遠係場大雨落完先見佢掛黃紅黑雨之類。<br />\n<br />\n香港雖然細，但地勢多變，居民又唔係集中喺同一個市中心，其實究竟暴雨同暴風信號實施分區制嘅話會唔會更好呢？<br />\n<br />\n可能有人話打風通常都係影響全港範圍，同埋八號波已有分四個方向，咁落雨就真係多數比較地區性，咁呢度講左暴雨先，有時新界北落全日雨而港島一直天晴，所以我認為起碼暴雨警告可以嘗試實行分區制：<br />\n<br />\n以下係小弟即刻整既少少劣作：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">全名：新界西北黃色暴雨警告<br />\n簡稱：西北黃雨警告</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/123458_6551e956ef888941b1439eaccaccef46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F123458_6551e956ef888941b1439eaccaccef46.jpg&h=d265e218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全名：市區及新界東南紅色暴雨警告<br />\n簡稱：東南黃雨警告</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/123459_f4dc3addf494dcd07d3443f72076b8d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F123459_f4dc3addf494dcd07d3443f72076b8d8.jpg&h=4235b212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全名：大嶼山及離島黑色暴雨警告<br />\n簡稱：離島黑雨警告<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/123500_615ea55f574fdd2f57080ed545454fdb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F123500_615ea55f574fdd2f57080ed545454fdb.jpg&h=53fadee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上既分區只係用嚟做例子，大家都可以講下應該點分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b27e4f4df8d4e820afa0649593809a252ab51eb","tid":332484,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"咁返工地方黑雨定係屋企黑雨唔洗返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483f20a7ce28d775b8de74ca188b6592833c09f8","tid":332484,"uid":35839,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁返工地方黑雨定係屋企黑雨唔洗返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人認為係兩個其中一個都唔洗，當然要睇個別工種同公司"},{"pid":"6c053684d83ab0eee6e21b6a5895df85423a3a18","tid":332484,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁返工地方黑雨定係屋企黑雨唔洗返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人認為係兩個其中一個都唔洗，當然要睇個別工種同公司</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abade58853cda3158dccc1b073c97c054f3f27a1","tid":332484,"uid":24589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁返工地方黑雨定係屋企黑雨唔洗返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人認為係兩個其中一個都唔洗，當然要睇個別工種同公司</blockquote><br />\n應該係either:<br />\n1) 兩個都紅 or<br />\n2) 其中一個黑<br />\n<br />\n對於學生黎講學校同屋企同區所以紅色就停得課"},{"pid":"6233746b8a571b237020667221a222f910bba59b","tid":332484,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T07:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁返工地方黑雨定係屋企黑雨唔洗返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人認為係兩個其中一個都唔洗，當然要睇個別工種同公司</blockquote><br />\n如果九龍區黑雨 我住將軍澳 每朝要搭巴士經過九龍去元朗返工呢？"},{"pid":"f277661ef092ff4c84f9ac39a6d91a852d6daf01","tid":332484,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:22:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁返工地方黑雨定係屋企黑雨唔洗返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人認為係兩個其中一個都唔洗，當然要睇個別工種同公司</blockquote><br />\n如果九龍區黑雨 我住將軍澳 每朝要搭巴士經過九龍去元朗返工呢？</blockquote><br />\n話知你死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大交合係咁幫打工仔就唔會假日先打八號波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}